summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 34E, page 99, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in G. Kinnear Addition, Lots 5 & 6, Block 11, Replat of Block 8, located on north side of W. Roy St. from line 1 lot east of 1st Ave. W. to alley west of 1st Ave. W. as Community Business (BC) Zone.
